attributes.title: worst app to be created EVER
attributes.review: this app is VERY BAD!! i recently got the app for obvious reasons and it’s the worst app thats ever been created on this earth. first of all, it takes so long for it to download that i’m left wondering for TWO WHOLE DAYS what’s taking so long. second, it takes up so much storage!! i think it takes up more storage than how much donald t. weighs (which is already A LOT)😡😡😡 Because of the unreasonable amount of storage it takes, my phone keeps crashing and glitching every time i open this app. even worse, when i opened the app for the first time i got a message from the app calling me rude names 👎 i will not go into details of the inappropriate names and words this app called me because i am still so traumatized and shocked by how out right terrible and disgusting this app truly is. furthermore, i think this app is secretly collecting my data to use against me as well as for all of the other people using this app 😳 i did not consent to that, and it is a violation!!! whoever came up with the idea, created, and paid for this app should be ASHAMED of themselves!!!!! they should delete this app off the app store IMMEDIATELY 😤🤮🤢 and not receive any money from this app!! or any support!! not to mention, the design and layout is super tacky 😪 this app is NOT user friendly, terrible, takes up too much storage, makes your phone glitch, and overall is just bad! very very bad! and whoever came up with the idea, created, and paid for this app is an absolute lunatic who needs to go to the doctor and get a cat scan to get their brain checked because they seriously need some help or therapy if this is the app and content they decided to have available 🥱😡👎
